<ion-view hide-tabs="true">
  <ion-header-bar class="bar headbar content-words">
    <label class="title">联系我们</label>
  </ion-header-bar>
  <ion-content style="background-color: #f6f5f5;">
    <div class="list contact-list">
      <div class="item item-nav">
        <div class="tabs" btn-active-directive="" single="true">
          <a class="tab-item active active-item">
            意见反馈
          </a>
          <a class="tab-item active-item">
            联系客服
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <ion-slide-box show-pager="false">
        <ion-slide>
          <div class="box blue">
            <div class="item item-clear">
              <p>你的建议和不满就是我们做得更好的动力！</p>
            </div>
            <div class="item item-input-inset">
              <textarea class="remark" placeholder="请输入你的建议" name="" id="" cols="30" rows="10"></textarea>
            </div>
            <div class="item item-clear">
              <p>你的联系方式</p>
            </div>
            <div class="item item-input-inset">
              <label class="item-input-wrapper input-clear">
                <input type="text" placeholder="手机号或者QQ">
              </label>
            </div>
            <div class="item item-clear">
              <div class="submit">
                <button class="button button-assertive button-block">
                  提交
                </button>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </ion-slide>
        <ion-slide>
          <div class="box yellow">
            <a class="item item-thumbnail-left" href="#">
              <img src="cover.jpg">
              <div style="text-align: center;">
                <h2>联系在线客服</h2>
                <p>在线对话，为你解决遇到的问题</p>
                <p>让我们愉快的交流吧！</p>
                <p>(08:00-23:00全年无休)</p>
              </div>
            </a>
            <a class="item item-thumbnail-left" href="#">
              <img src="cover.jpg">
              <div style="text-align: center;">
                <h2>拨打官方热线</h2>
                <p>400-0000-000</p>
                <p>(09:00-21:00全年无休)</p>
              </div>
            </a>
            <div class="item item-clear">
              <p>电话占线？非客服服务时间？ <a href="#" ui-sref="tabs.help">常见问题点这里</a></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </ion-slide>
      </ion-slide-box>
    </div>
  </ion-content>
</ion-view>